quoteFirst: Sized up the candidates for the ball team. No good. Four forty P. M. Tom Clifton received notification to that effect.
quoteLast: Tom Clifton said so much in about three minutes that I left it all out. Four fifty P. M.
title: The Rambler Club's ball nine
author: Sheppard, W. Crispin (William Crispin), 1871-
